title: How to Make a Low Calorie Faygo Pop Cake

steps.headline: Decide you want to make a delicious low calorie and low fat cake.
Combine cake mix and Faygo Pop well.
Spray pan with non-stick cooking spray.
Test cake with Toothpick to see if cake is ready.
Remove from oven and allow cake to air cool.
Frost cake with a rubber spatula.
Eat mouth-watering and scrumptious Low Calorie Faygo Pop Cake.
Make pudding as directed on the package except use fat free milk.
Allow to set as instructed on the box.
Fold light cool whip into pudding.

text: Cake Decide you want to make a delicious low calorie and low fat cake.  Preheat oven to 350 degrees.  Combine cake mix and Faygo Pop well.  Spray pan with non-stick cooking spray.  Pour into cake pan.  Bake for about 20 to 25 minutes.  Test cake with Toothpick to see if cake is ready.  Remove from oven and allow cake to air cool.  Frost cake with a rubber spatula.  Eat mouth-watering and scrumptious Low Calorie Faygo Pop Cake.  Frosting Make pudding as directed on the package except use fat free milk.  Allow to set as instructed on the box.  Fold light cool whip into pudding.
